title: Ebro In The Morning - Into the Whites + Guest Andrew Yang
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/17.

Ebro sounds off on the colorism displayed in Into the Heights, Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (17), and NYC Mayoral Candidate Andrew Yang joins the Crew (29:00). The Crew gives away Summer Jam Tickets and talks Mayors (1:00:00).
